-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- POST DRUID ALCHEMY PATH (699)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Step 1: Introduction to alchemy path
queststatus(691) = 5, queststatus(699) = 0, english, "alchemist"-> queststatus(699) = 1, "Alchemy is a discipline. It relies on balance, careful observation, and precise methods. A careless hand can ruin a mixture or worse. If you wish to learn, we will begin with the fundamentals. Ask me how to brew your first potion and I will guide you along the path.", inform("[Hint] Fianna's lesson will guide you through how to craft a simple ruby potion. Ask her about your first potion.")
queststatus(691) = 5, queststatus(699) = 0, "alchemy", "potion", "brew" -> queststatus(699) = 1, "Alchemy is a discipline. It relies on balance, careful observation, and precise methods. A careless hand can ruin a mixture or worse. If you wish to learn, we will begin with the fundamentals. Ask me how to brew your first potion and I will guide you along the path.", inform("[Hint] Fianna's lesson will guide you through how to craft a simple ruby potion. Ask her about your first potion.")
queststatus(691) = 5, queststatus(699) = 0, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen" ->queststatus(699) = 1, "Alchemie ist eine Disziplin. Sie beruht auf Gleichgewicht, sorgfõltiger Beobachtung und prõzisen Methoden. Eine unachtsame Hand kann eine Mischung verderben oder Schlimmeres verursachen. Wenn du lernen m÷chtest, beginnen wir mit den Grundlagen. Frage mich, wie du deinen ersten Trank brauen kannst, und ich werde dich auf diesem Weg f³hren.", inform("[Hinweis] Fiannas Lektion wird dich durch den Prozess f³hren, wie man einen einfachen Rubin-Trank herstellt. Frage sie nach deinem ersten Trank.")

-- Step 2: Give sickle and collect sprouts
queststatus(699) = 1, english, "alchemist" -> item(126, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 2, "Then we begin simply. Take this sickle and gather fir sprouts from the fir tree behind me. Even one untrained in herblore can harvest them. Bring me at least four sprouts for this simple potion."
queststatus(699) = 1, "alchemy", "potion", "brew" -> item(126, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 2, "Then we begin simply. Take this sickle and gather fir sprouts from the fir tree behind me. Even one untrained in herblore can harvest them. Bring me at least four sprouts for this simple potion."
queststatus(699) = 1, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen" -> item(126, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 2, "Dann beginnen wir ganz einfach. Nimm diese Sichel und sammle Tannensprossen von der Tanne hinter mir. Selbst jemand ohne Kenntnisse in der Krõuterkunde kann sie ernten. Bring mir mindestens vier Sprossen f³r diesen einfachen Trank."

-- Step 3: Turn in sprouts and explain herb difficulty
queststatus(699) = 2, item(149, all) > 3, english, "alchemist" -> queststatus(699) = 3, "Good. These sprouts are simple to prepare. In alchemy we sort herbs by their stage of maturity. Sprout Herbs are the simplest, followed by Young Herbs, Mature Herbs, and finally Elder Herbs, which require the greatest care and attention. Shall we continue making your first potion?", inform("[Hint] Herb difficulty tiers - ((0-25)) Sprout Herbs, ((26-50)) Young Herbs, ((51-75)) Mature Herbs, ((76-100)) Elder Herbs).")
queststatus(699) = 2, item(149, all) > 3, "alchemy", "sprout", "fir", "potion", "gather", "brew" -> queststatus(699) = 3, "Good. These sprouts are simple to prepare. In alchemy we sort herbs by their stage of maturity. Sprout Herbs are the simplest, followed by Young Herbs, Mature Herbs, and finally Elder Herbs, which require the greatest care and attention. Shall we continue making your first potion?", inform("[Hint] Herb difficulty tiers - ((0-25)) Sprout Herbs, ((26-50)) Young Herbs, ((51-75)) Mature Herbs, ((76-100)) Elder Herbs). Ask about potions to continue...")
queststatus(699) = 2, item(149, all) > 3, "alchemist", "alchemie", "sprossen", "tannen", "trank", "ernten", "brauen" -> "Gut. Diese Sprossen lassen sich leicht vorbereiten. In der Alchemie sortieren wir Krõuter nach ihrem Reifestadium. Spross-Krõuter sind die einfachsten, gefolgt von Jungen Krõutern, Reifen Krõutern und schlie▀lich Alten Krõutern, die die gr÷▀te Sorgfalt und Aufmerksamkeit erfordern. Sollen wir mit der Herstellung deines ersten Tranks weitermachen?", inform("[Hinweis] Schwierigkeitsstufen der Krõuter ? ((0?25)) Spross-Krõuter, ((26?50)) Junge Krõuter, ((51?75)) Reife Krõuter, ((76?100)) Alte Krõuter. Frage nach Trõnken, um fortzufahren?")

-- Step 4: Not enough sprouts
queststatus(699) = 2, english, "alchemist" -> "You have not gathered enough sprouts yet. Use the sickle near the fir tree behind me to gather at least four sprouts."
queststatus(699) = 2, "alchemy", "sprout", "fir", "potion", "gather", "brew" -> "You have not gathered enough sprouts yet. Use the sickle near the fir tree behind me to gather at least four sprouts."
queststatus(699) = 2, "alchemist", "alchemie", "sprossen", "tannen", "trank", "ernten", "brauen" -> "Du hast noch nicht gen³gend Sprossen gesammelt. Benutze die Sichel an der Tanne hinter mir, um mindestens vier Sprossen zu sammeln."

-- Step 5: Give bucket to collect water
queststatus(699) = 3, english, "alchemist" -> item(51, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 4, "Now we need a clean medium to serve as a foundation for our potion. Please, take this bucket and find the purest source of water and fill it carefully. Seek deep wells, blessed lakes, or clear running water. Never stale waters or swamps!"
queststatus(699) = 3, "alchemy", "potion", "brew" -> item(51, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 4, "Now we need a clean medium to serve as a foundation for our potion. Please, take this bucket and find the purest source of water and fill it carefully. Seek deep wells, blessed lakes, or clear running water. Never stale waters or swamps!"
queststatus(699) = 3, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen" ->  item(51, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 4,"Nun brauchen wir ein sauberes Medium, das als Grundlage f³r unseren Trank dient. Nimm bitte diesen Eimer und finde die reinste Wasserquelle, um ihn sorgfõltig zu f³llen. Suche tiefe Brunnen, gesegnete Seen oder klares flie▀endes Wasser. Niemals stehendes Wasser oder S³mpfe!"

-- Step 6: Bucket filled
queststatus(699) = 4, item(52, all) > 0, english, "alchemist" -> queststatus(699) = 5, "Well done. Many aspiring alchemists forget the importance of water. Impure water weakens a brew before it is even begun. Remember this. Speak with me again and we will prepare your first potion."
queststatus(699) = 4, item(52, all) > 0, "alchemy", "water", "bucket", "potion", "brew" -> queststatus(699) = 5, "Well done. Many aspiring alchemists forget the importance of water. Impure water weakens a brew before it is even begun. Remember this. Speak with me again and we will prepare your first potion."
queststatus(699) = 4, item(52, all) > 0, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen", "wasser", "eimer" -> queststatus(699) = 5, "Gut gemacht. Viele angehende Alchemisten vergessen die Bedeutung von Wasser. Unreines Wasser schwõcht einen Trank, bevor er ³berhaupt begonnen wurde. Merke dir das. Sprich wieder mit mir, und wir werden deinen ersten Trank zubereiten."

-- Step 7: Bucket not filled
queststatus(699) = 4, english, "alchemist" -> "The bucket is still empty. Find a source of clean water and fill it before returning to me."
queststatus(699) = 4, "alchemy", "water", "bucket", "potion", "brew" -> "The bucket is still empty. Find a source of clean water and fill it before returning to me."
queststatus(699) = 4, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen", "wasser", "eimer"  -> "Der Eimer ist noch leer. Finde eine Quelle mit sauberem Wasser und f³lle ihn, bevor du zu mir zur³ckkehrst."

-- Step 8: Brewing first stock
queststatus(699) = 5, english, "alchemist" -> item(58, 1, 555), item(164, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 6, "Let us begin. Take this mortar and an empty bottle. Hold the mortar and stand before the cauldron. Add water first, then four fir sprouts, and fill the bottle. When a mixture of herbs settles into a medium of water, this is called a stock, tell me to look at your potion when ready.", inform("[Hint] There is a cauldron nearby, ensure no one else is currently using it. If it is abandoned but not empty, you can use a water bucket to clean it, don't forget to refill! Face the cauldron with the mortar in your hand, add water, then double click the ingredients one by one and wait for the action to finish: bucket of water, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, then empty bottle.")
queststatus(699) = 5, "alchemy", "potion", "brew" -> item(58, 1, 555), item(164, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 6, "Let us begin. Take this mortar and an empty bottle. Hold the mortar and stand before the cauldron. Add water first, then four fir sprouts, and fill the bottle. When a mixture of herbs settles into a medium of water, this is called a stock, tell me to look at your potion when ready.", inform("[Hint] There is a cauldron nearby, ensure no one else is currently using it. If it is abandoned but not empty, you can use a water bucket to clean it, don't forget to refill! Face the cauldron with the mortar in your hand, add water, then double click the ingredients one by one and wait for the action to finish: bucket of water, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, then empty bottle.")
queststatus(699) = 5, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen" -> item(58, 1, 555), item(164, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 6, "Lass uns beginnen. Nimm diesen M÷rser und eine leere Flasche. Halte den M÷rser und stelle dich vor den Kessel. Gib zuerst Wasser hinzu, dann vier Tannensprossen, und f³lle die Flasche. Wenn sich eine Mischung aus Krõutern in einem Wasser-Medium absetzt, nennt man dies eine Basisl÷sung. Sage mir Bescheid, wenn dein Trank fertig ist, damit ich ihn ansehen kann.", inform("[Hinweis] In der Nõhe befindet sich ein Kessel; stelle sicher, dass ihn gerade niemand benutzt. Wenn er frei, aber noch nicht leer ist, kannst du ihn mit einem Eimer Wasser reinigen - vergiss nicht, ihn anschlie▀end wieder zu f³llen! Stelle dich mit dem M÷rser in der Hand vor den Kessel, f³ge Wasser hinzu, und doppelklicke dann die Zutaten einzeln, wõhrend du auf den Abschluss jeder Aktion wartest: Eimer Wasser, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, anschlie▀end die leere Flasche.")

-- Step 9: Stock created - checking for +4 perc(Highly toxic Hyperborelium) -4 const(Saturated Echolon) 
queststatus(699) = 6, item(331, all, "AdrazinConcentration" = "5", "IllidriumConcentration" = "5", "CaprazinConcentration" = "5", "HyperboreliumConcentration" = "9", "EcholonConcentration" = "1", "DracolinConcentration" = "5", "OrcanolConcentration" = "5", "FenolinConcentration" = "5") > 0, english, "alchemist" -> item(46, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 7, "Good work. Never drink a stock. Instead, inspect it through this ruby. Each harvestable herb carries two concentrated properties or substances: saturation and toxicity. These lie at opposite ends of the same scale, so equal measures will cancel each other. Take care never to let either rise beyond four applications, or the stock may grow unstable and cause harm.", inform("[Hint] Use the ruby with your stock in a hand slot. Water rests at a balance of (5). Herbs shift this balance. In this mixture you should see Highly Toxic Hyperborelium (9) and Saturated Echolon (1). Equal measures move the balance back toward (5). Never allow a substance to pass four steps from this balance.")
queststatus(699) = 6, item(331, all, "AdrazinConcentration" = "5", "IllidriumConcentration" = "5", "CaprazinConcentration" = "5", "HyperboreliumConcentration" = "9", "EcholonConcentration" = "1", "DracolinConcentration" = "5", "OrcanolConcentration" = "5", "FenolinConcentration" = "5") > 0, "alchemy", "potion", "brew", "stock" -> item(46, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 7, "Good work. Never drink a stock. Instead, inspect it through this ruby. Each harvestable herb carries two concentrated properties or substances: saturation and toxicity. These lie at opposite ends of the same scale, so equal measures will cancel each other. Take care never to let either rise beyond four applications, or the stock may grow unstable and cause harm.", inform("[Hint] Use the ruby with your stock in a hand slot. Water rests at a balance of (5). Herbs shift this balance. In this mixture you should see Highly Toxic Hyperborelium (9) and Saturated Echolon (1). Equal measures move the balance back toward (5). Never allow a substance to pass four steps from this balance.")
queststatus(699) = 6, item(331, all, "AdrazinConcentration" = "5", "IllidriumConcentration" = "5", "CaprazinConcentration" = "5", "HyperboreliumConcentration" = "9", "EcholonConcentration" = "1", "DracolinConcentration" = "5", "OrcanolConcentration" = "5", "FenolinConcentration" = "5") > 0, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen", "basisl÷sung" -> item(46, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 7, "Gut gemacht. Trinke eine Basisl÷sung niemals. Stattdessen untersuche sie mit diesem Rubin. Jedes erntbare Kraut trõgt zwei konzentrierte Eigenschaften oder Substanzen: Sõttigung und Toxizitõt. Diese liegen an gegen³berliegenden Enden derselben Skala, sodass gleiche Mengen sich gegenseitig aufheben. Achte darauf, dass keine der beiden Eigenschaften mehr als vier Anwendungen ³berschreitet, sonst kann die Basisl÷sung instabil werden und Schaden verursachen.", inform("[Hinweis] Benutze den Rubin zusammen mit deiner Basisl÷sung im Hand-Slot. Wasser liegt im Gleichgewicht bei (5). Krõuter verschieben dieses Gleichgewicht. In dieser Mischung solltest du Hochgiftiges Hyperborelium (9) und Gesõttigtes Echolon (1) sehen. Gleiche Mengen bringen das Gleichgewicht wieder in Richtung (5). Lass keine Substanz jemals mehr als vier Schritte von diesem Gleichgewicht abweichen.")

-- Step 10: stock not created correctly or lost
queststatus(699) = 6, english, "alchemist" -> "You have not created the necessary stock. Stand before the cauldron with the mortar. Add the water, four fir sprouts, then bottle. If you lack reagents I can sell you the basics. Tell me you have the potion stock to continue.", inform("[Hint] There is a cauldron nearby, ensure no one else is currently using it. If it is abandoned but not empty, you can use a water bucket to clean it, don't forget to refill! Face the cauldron with the mortar in your hand, add water, then double click the ingredients one by one and wait for the action to finish: bucket of water, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, then empty bottle.")
queststatus(699) = 6, "alchemy", "potion", "brew" -> "You have not created the necessary stock. Stand before the cauldron with the mortar. Add the water, four fir sprouts, then bottle. If you lack reagents I can sell you the basics. Tell me you have the potion stock to continue.", inform("[Hint] There is a cauldron nearby, ensure no one else is currently using it. If it is abandoned but not empty, you can use a water bucket to clean it, don't forget to refill! Face the cauldron with the mortar in your hand, add water, then double click the ingredients one by one and wait for the action to finish: bucket of water, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, then empty bottle.")
queststatus(699) = 6, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen" -> "Du hast die notwendige Basisl÷sung noch nicht hergestellt. Stelle dich mit dem M÷rser vor den Kessel. Gib zuerst das Wasser, dann vier Tannensprossen und schlie▀lich die Flasche hinzu. Wenn dir die Zutaten fehlen, kann ich dir die Grundlagen verkaufen. Sage mir, dass du die Basisl÷sung hast, um fortzufahren.", inform("[Hinweis] In der Nõhe befindet sich ein Kessel; stelle sicher, dass ihn gerade niemand benutzt. Wenn er frei, aber noch nicht leer ist, kannst du ihn mit einem Eimer Wasser reinigen - vergiss nicht, ihn anschlie▀end wieder zu f³llen! Stelle dich mit dem M÷rser in der Hand vor den Kessel, f³ge Wasser hinzu, und doppelklicke dann die Zutaten einzeln, wõhrend du auf den Abschluss jeder Aktion wartest: Eimer Wasser, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, anschlie▀end die leere Flasche.")

-- Step 11: Finish the potion
queststatus(699) = 7, english, "alchemist" -> queststatus(699) = 8, item(447, 1, 555), "Now lets finish your first potion before we examine it. Add your stock back to the cauldron, then add this ruby powder, and bottle it again. Tell me you are done with the potion.", inform("[Hint] Just stand in front of the empty cauldron, double-click the green potion stock to add it back to the cauldron, then add ruby powder, rebottle, and say potion to Fianna.")
queststatus(699) = 7, "alchemy", "potion", "brew" -> queststatus(699) = 8, item(447, 1, 555), "Now lets finish your first potion before we examine it. Add your stock back to the cauldron, then add this ruby powder, and bottle it again. Tell me you are done with the potion.", inform("[Hint] Just stand in front of the empty cauldron, double-click the green potion stock to add it back to the cauldron, then add ruby powder, rebottle, and say potion to Fianna.")
queststatus(699) = 7, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen" -> queststatus(699) = 8, item(447, 1, 555), "Nun lass uns deinen ersten Trank fertigstellen, bevor wir ihn untersuchen. Gib deine Basisl÷sung zur³ck in den Kessel, f³ge dann dieses Rubinpulver hinzu und f³lle die Flasche erneut. Sage mir, wenn du mit dem Trank fertig bist.", inform("[Hinweis] Stelle dich einfach vor den leeren Kessel, doppelklicke die gr³ne Basisl÷sung, um sie wieder in den Kessel zu geben, f³ge dann das Rubinpulver hinzu, f³lle die Flasche erneut und sage Trank zu Fianna.")

-- Step 12: Potion examination explained
queststatus(699) = 8, item(59, all, "potionEffectId" = "55591555") > 0, english, "alchemist" -> item(46, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 9, "Like examining a stock, potions and- later- essence brews can be examined with the same color gemstone as the powder used. For ruby, you will be able to see each of the eight substances, how the fir sprouts effected concentrations, and the potion's quality. Don't drink it yet ask more about potions!", inform("[Hint] You should now be able to see the potion's quality, highly toxic Hyperborelium and saturated Echolon, and the unaffected, neutral substances. Ask more about potions.")
queststatus(699) = 8, item(59, all, "potionEffectId" = "55591555") > 0, "alchemy", "examine", "potion" -> item(46, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 9, "Like examining a stock, potions and- later- essence brews can be examined with the same color gemstone as the powder used. For ruby, you will be able to see each of the eight substances, how the fir sprouts effected concentrations, and the potion's quality. Don't drink it yet ask more about potions!", inform("[Hint] You should now be able to see the potion's quality, highly toxic Hyperborelium and saturated Echolon, and the unaffected, neutral substances. Ask more about potions.")
queststatus(699) = 8, item(59, all, "potionEffectId" = "55591555") > 0, "alchemist", "alchemie", "untersuch", "trank" -> item(46, 1, 555), queststatus(699) = 9, "Wie beim Untersuchen einer Basisl÷sung k÷nnen Trõnke und ? spõter ? Essenzmischungen mit demselben farbigen Edelstein wie das verwendete Pulver untersucht werden. Bei Rubin kannst du jede der acht Substanzen sehen, wie die Tannensprossen die Konzentrationen beeinflusst haben, und die Qualitõt des Tranks erkennen. Trinke ihn noch nicht, frage erst weiter nach Trõnken!", inform("[Hinweis] Du solltest jetzt die Qualitõt des Tranks sehen k÷nnen, das hochgiftige Hyperborelium und das gesõttigte Echolon sowie die unbeeinflussten, neutralen Substanzen. Frage weiter nach Trõnken.")

-- Step 13: Potion not present
queststatus(699) = 8, english, "alchemist" -> "You don't have the right potion to examine. I can sell you more supplies but you will need to harvest four fir sprouts from the fir tree beind me.", inform("[Hint] Pick four fir sprouts, stand in front of the cauldron, ensure no one else is currently using it. If it is abandoned but not empty, you can use a water bucket to clean it, don't forget to refill! Face the cauldron with the mortar in your hand, add water, then double click the ingredients one by one and wait for the action to finish: bucket of water, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, ruby powder, then empty bottle.")
queststatus(699) = 8, "alchemy", "examine", "ruby", "potion" -> "You don't have the right potion to examine. I can sell you more supplies but you will need to harvest four fir sprouts from the fir tree behind me.", inform("[Hint] Pick four fir sprouts, stand in front of the cauldron, ensure no one else is currently using it. If it is abandoned but not empty, you can use a water bucket to clean it, don't forget to refill! Face the cauldron with the mortar in your hand, add water, then double click the ingredients one by one and wait for the action to finish: bucket of water, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, fir sprout, ruby powder, then empty bottle.")
queststatus(699) = 8, "alchemist" ,"alchemie", "untersuch", "rubin", "trank" -> "Du hast nicht den richtigen Trank zum Untersuchen. Ich kann dir weitere Vorrõte verkaufen, aber du musst zuerst vier Tannensprossen von der Tanne hinter mir sammeln.", inform("[Hinweis] Pfl³cke vier Tannensprossen und stelle dich vor den Kessel. Stelle sicher, dass ihn gerade niemand benutzt. Wenn er frei, aber noch nicht leer ist, kannst du ihn mit einem Eimer Wasser reinigen ? vergiss nicht, ihn anschlie▀end wieder zu f³llen! Stelle dich mit dem M÷rser in der Hand vor den Kessel, f³ge Wasser hinzu, und doppelklicke dann die Zutaten nacheinander, wõhrend du auf den Abschluss jeder Aktion wartest: Eimer Wasser, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, Tannensprosse, Rubinpulver, dann die leere Flasche.")

-- Step 14: Making a recipe explained
queststatus(699) = 9, english, "alchemist" -> queststatus(699) = 10, item(463, 1, 555), item(2745, 1, 555), "Many alchemists keep parchment and quill to record their recipes. Writing them down helps ensure the mixture can be repeated correctly. Half-Hung outside the Inn sells both, but here, take these if you wish to practice and keep asking me about potions!.", inform("[Hint] To write a recipe(Or alter it) hold both the quill and an empty parchment, or the recipe to be altered, in your hand slots. Double click the quill, select -alchemy- then -Write an alchemy recipe-, and add the steps one by one. Later you can find players to make you books. Ask about potions to continue.")
queststatus(699) = 9, "alchemy", "potion", "brew" -> queststatus(699) = 10, item(463, 1, 555), item(2745, 1, 555), "Many alchemists keep parchment and quill to record their recipes. Writing them down helps ensure the mixture can be repeated correctly. Half-Hung outside the Inn sells both, but here, take these if you wish to practice and keep asking me about potions!.", inform("[Hint] To write a recipe(Or alter it) hold both the quill and an empty parchment, or the recipe to be altered, in your hand slots. Double click the quill, select -alchemy- then -Write an alchemy recipe-, and add the steps one by one. Later you can find players to make you books. Ask about potions to continue.")
queststatus(699) = 9, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen" ->  queststatus(699) = 10, item(463, 1, 555), item(2745, 1, 555), "Viele Alchemisten f³hren Pergament und Feder, um ihre Rezepte aufzuschreiben. Das Aufzeichnen hilft, sicherzustellen, dass die Mischung korrekt wiederholt werden kann. Half-Hung au▀erhalb des Gasthauses verkauft beides, aber hier, nimm diese, wenn du ³ben m÷chtest, und frage mich weiterhin nach Trõnken!", inform("[Hinweis] Um ein Rezept zu schreiben (oder zu õndern), halte sowohl die Feder als auch ein leeres Pergament ? oder das Rezept, das geõndert werden soll ? in deinen Hand-Slots. Doppelklicke die Feder, wõhle Alchemie und dann Ein Alchemie-Rezept schreiben, und f³ge die Schritte einzeln hinzu. Spõter kannst du andere Spieler finden, die dir B³cher herstellen. Frage nach Trõnken, um fortzufahren.")

-- Step 15: Second potion preparation
queststatus(699) = 10, english, "alchemist" -> item(164, 1, 555), item(197, 1, 555), item(450, 1, 555), item(133, 4, 555), queststatus(699) = 11, "Now we try another mixture. Take these sun herbs, amethyst powder, and a new bottle. Brew as before. Before you add the amethyst powder, drink the ruby potion you made earlier! It will sharpen your senses for this task. Ask about your potion to continue.", inform("[Hint] Pay close attention to the effects you feel when you drink the ruby potion. Alchemy is about exploring different effects of herbs!")
queststatus(699) = 10, "alchemy", "potion", "brew" -> item(164, 1, 555), item(197, 1, 555), item(450, 1, 555), item(133, 4, 555), queststatus(699) = 11, "Now we try another mixture. Take these sun herbs, amethyst powder, and a new bottle. Brew as before. Before you add the amethyst powder, drink the ruby potion you made earlier! It will sharpen your senses for this task. Ask about your potion to continue.", inform("[Hint] Pay close attention to the effects you feel when you drink the ruby potion. Alchemy is about exploring different effects of herbs!")
queststatus(699) = 10, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen" -> item(164, 1, 555), item(197, 1, 555), item(450, 1, 555), item(133, 4, 555), queststatus(699) = 11, "Nun probieren wir eine weitere Mischung. Nimm diese Sonnenkrõuter, Amethystpulver und eine neue Flasche. Braue wie zuvor. Bevor du das Amethystpulver hinzuf³gst, trinke den Rubin-Trank, den du zuvor hergestellt hast! Er wird deine Sinne f³r diese Aufgabe schõrfen. Frage nach deinem Trank, um fortzufahren.", inform("[Hinweis] Achte genau auf die Effekte, die du beim Trinken des Rubin-Tranks sp³rst. Alchemie dreht sich darum, die unterschiedlichen Wirkungen von Krõutern zu erforschen!")

-- Step 16: Health potion created
queststatus(699) = 11, item(166, all, "potionEffectId" = "95555515") > 0, english, "alchemist" -> queststatus(699) = 12, "Excellent. This brew restores health quickly but drains food over time. Use the amethyst to examine it. In amethyst brews the quality affects the strength of the effect. Potions also leave toxins within the body so drink them with care."
queststatus(699) = 11, item(166, all, "potionEffectId" = "95555515") > 0, "alchemy", "potion", "brew", "examine" -> queststatus(699) = 12, "Excellent. This brew restores health quickly but drains food over time. Use the amethyst to examine it. In amethyst brews the quality affects the strength of the effect. Potions also leave toxins within the body so drink them with care."
queststatus(699) = 11, item(166, all, "potionEffectId" = "95555515") > 0, "alchemist", "alchemie", "trank", "brauen", "untersuch" -> queststatus(699) = 12, "Ausgezeichnet. Dieser Trank stellt die Gesundheit schnell wieder her, verbraucht aber mit der Zeit Nahrung. Benutze den Amethyst, um ihn zu untersuchen. Bei Amethyst-Trõnken beeinflusst die Qualitõt die Stõrke der Wirkung. Trõnke hinterlassen zudem Toxine im K÷rper, also trinke sie mit Vorsicht."

