queststatus(691) = 1, "Galmair contact", "Galmair druid", "Galmair weaver" -> "The contact in Galmair is Grator Bottlebreak; look outside the alchemy hall near the main gate."
queststatus(691) = 1, "Galmair-Kontakt", "Galmair-Druide", "Galmair-Weber", "Galmair Kontakt", "Galmair Druide", "Galmair Weber" -> "Der Kontakt in Galmair ist Grator Bottlebreak; sieh au▀erhalb der Alchemiehalle in der Nõhe des Haupttors nach."

